# Backend API base URL.
# • Leave EMPTY for local dev – Vite proxy forwards /api → localhost:3001.
# • Leave EMPTY for single-Web-App deployment – the Express backend serves
#   the built frontend, so the browser uses a relative '/api' on the same origin.
# • Only set this if the API is on a DIFFERENT host (e.g. separate backend app).
VITE_API_URL=
VITE_COMPANY_NAME=Stark Industries
